<title>Welcome to LWC Communities!</title>

<style>

		-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;

	body {

		}

			padding-bottom: var(--rpl-sp-12);
			padding-top: var(--rpl-sp-12);
		}

	.docs-inverted-background,

		background-color: var(--rpl-clr-primary-alt);
	}

	.docs-background--neutral-100 {
		background-color: var(--rpl-clr-neutral-100);
	}

		--dxp-s-section-content-spacing-block-end: 2rem;
		--dxp-s-section-content-spacing-inline-start: 2rem;
		--dxp-s-section-content-spacing-inline-end: 2rem;
	}

	.docs-header .docs-header-logo img {
		height: 48px;
	}

	.rpl-footer-logo-link__img {
		height: 48px
	}

	.rpl-footer-vic-gov-logo {
		display: none
	}

	/* fix for example primary navs which are not in the header */

	main .rpl-primary-nav {
		margin-top: -4px; }

	.app-wysiwyg table code {
		overflow-wrap: break-word;
		word-wrap: break-word;
		word-break: break-all;
	}


	/* mini SLDS */
	.slds-button--icon, .slds-button--icon-border, .slds-button--icon-border-filled, .slds-button--icon-border-inverse,

		color: var(--slds-g-color-neutral-base-50,#747474);
		-ms-flex-negative: 0;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.slds-button {
		position: relative;
		display: -webkit-inline-box;
		display: -ms-inline-flexbox;
		display: inline-flex;
		-webkit-box-align: center;
		-ms-flex-align: center;

		background: none;
		background-color: var(--slds-c-button-color-background,var(--sds-c-button-color-background,transparent));

		border: var(--slds-c-button-sizing-border,var(--sds-c-button-sizing-border,1px)) solid var(--slds-c-button-color-border,var(--sds-c-button-color-border,transparent));
		border-radius: var(--slds-c-button-radius-border,var(--sds-c-button-radius-border,.25rem));
		-webkit-box-shadow: var(--slds-c-button-shadow,var(--sds-c-button-shadow));

		line-height: var(--slds-c-button-line-height,var(--sds-c-button-line-height,1.875rem));

		-webkit-appearance: none;
		white-space: normal;
		-webkit-user-select: none;
		-moz-user-select: none;
        -ms-user-select: none;
		user-select: none;
	}

	.slds-button__icon {
        width: .875rem;
		height: .875rem;
		fill: var(--slds-c-icon-color-foreground,currentColor);
	}

	.slds-assistive-text {
		position: absolute!important;
        margin: -1px!important;
		border: 0!important;
		padding: 0!important;
		width: 1px!important;
		height: 1px!important;
		overflow: hidden!important;
		clip: rect(0 0 0 0)!important;
		text-transform: none!important;
		white-space: nowrap!important;
	}
</style>
